    Description

    DirectoryIterator
    The DirectoryIterator class provides a way to iterate through a list of directory paths.
    ExplorerCollection
    The ExplorerCollection interface defines the contract for creating an iterator that can traverse a collection of directories.
    ExplorerContainer
     
    File
     
    FileChooserDemo
    The FileChooserDemo class demonstrates a GUI application for selecting a ZIP file and extracting its contents using a custom ZIP extraction utility.
    FileExplorerIterator
    The FileExplorerIterator interface defines the contract for an iterator that traverses through a collection of files or directories.
    TestResultObserver
    The TestResultObserver interface defines a contract for objects that want to be notified of updates related to test results.
    TestResults
    The TestResults class implements the TestResultObserver interface and serves as a container for storing and managing test results, including marks, feedback, and test names.
    TestRunner
     
    TestSubject
    The TestSubject interface defines the methods for a subject that can notify an observer about changes or updates, specifically in the context of test results.

    ZipExtractor
    The ZipExtractor class handles the extraction of ZIP files, including nested zip files, and stores the directories of student submissions.
